## Stage Relationships

```
01-requirement
  consumes: User Requirement
  produces: REQ, PS
  ↓
02-development
  consumes: REQ, PS
  produces: TS, AD, US, TASK, FI, BI
  ↓
03-testing
  consumes: FI, BI, TC
  produces: TR, QEP
  ↓
04-release
  consumes: QEP, DRR
  produces: SDP
  ↓
05-feedback
  consumes: SDP, Production Incidents
  produces: New REQ
  ↓
  (back to 01-requirement)
```
